params._planetOrbit: Orbit tier of the planet From Spreadsheet: Stardust earned per expedition = (((planet_level -1) ^ 2) * level_parameter + 1) * ((planet_rarity -1) * rarity_parameter + 1) * stardust_base_rate Planet orbit will always start from 1. Hence, planetOrbit which is planet_rarity, will need to + 1 to match the equation.
